graph TB
    subgraph Operator["Llama Stack K8s Operator"]
        direction TB
        Controller["Reconciler Controller<br/>(controller-runtime)"]
        Kustomizer["Kustomize Pipeline<br/>(in-process rendering)"]
        CABundle["CA Bundle Manager<br/>(PEM parsing, X.509 validation)"]
        StatusProbe["Status Probe<br/>(/v1/health, /v1/providers, /v1/version)"]
        FeatureFlags["Feature Flags<br/>(ConfigMap-based)"]
        MetricsProxy["kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS"]

        Controller -->|renders manifests via| Kustomizer
        Controller -->|aggregates certs via| CABundle
        Controller -->|probes server via| StatusProbe
        Controller -->|reads flags from| FeatureFlags
    end

    User[Data Scientist / Admin] -->|creates/updates| LLSDCR["LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>(llamastack.io/v1alpha1)"]
    LLSDCR -->|watched by| Controller

    subgraph ManagedResources["Managed Per-Instance Resources"]
        direction TB
        Deployment["Deployment<br/>(Llama Stack server)"]
        Service["Service<br/>(ClusterIP 8321/TCP)"]
        SA["ServiceAccount"]
        PVC["PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>(optional)"]
        NP["NetworkPolicy<br/>(feature-flagged)"]
        PDB["PodDisruptionBudget"]
        HPA["HorizontalPodAutoscaler<br/>(optional)"]
        RB["RoleBinding<br/>(anyuid SCC)"]
        Ingress["Ingress<br/>(optional, exposeRoute=true)"]
        CAConfigMap["CA Bundle ConfigMap<br/>({instance}-ca-bundle)"]
    end

    Kustomizer -->|creates/updates| Deployment
    Kustomizer -->|creates/updates| Service
    Kustomizer -->|creates/updates| SA
    Kustomizer -->|creates/updates| PVC
    Kustomizer -->|creates/updates| NP
    Kustomizer -->|creates/updates| PDB
    Kustomizer -->|creates/updates| HPA
    Kustomizer -->|creates/updates| RB
    Controller -->|creates/updates| Ingress
    CABundle -->|creates/updates| CAConfigMap

    Controller -->|CRUD operations| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"]
    StatusProbe -->|queries| LLSDPod["Llama Stack Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP"]

    ODHCAbundle["odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>ConfigMap"] -->|auto-detected by| CABundle
    UserConfigMap["User ConfigMaps<br/>(spec.server.config)"] -.->|read by| Controller
    OperatorConfig["llama-stack-operator-config<br/>ConfigMap"] -->|configures| FeatureFlags
    Prometheus["Prometheus"] -->|scrapes| MetricsProxy

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style Kustomizer fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style CABundle fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style StatusProbe fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style FeatureFlags fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style MetricsProxy fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style LLSDCR fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style Deployment fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style Service fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style SA fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style PVC fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style NP fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style PDB fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style HPA fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style RB fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style Ingress fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style CAConfigMap fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style LLSDPod fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style ODHCAbundle fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style UserConfigMap fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style OperatorConfig fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
